cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.NE, cs.SY

The paper discusses the application of deep learning models, specifically WaveNet, for energy disaggregation and on/off detection of household appliances. This falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. The paper also deals with time series data, which is covered by cs.SD (signal processing) and cs.NE (neural and evolutionary computing). Finally, the paper deals with the control and monitoring of household appliances, which falls under the category of control systems, covered by cs.SY.
